<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8012563>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Timonius megalocalyx. A. Habit, leafy branch with fruits. B. Young twig showing stipules at shoot apex. C. Close-up of lower leaf surface. D. Stipules in transverse section showing aestivation. E. Staminate inflorescence. F. Staminate corolla bud, in transverse section showing imbricate aestivation. G. Fruit. H. Fruit, in transverse section.A–C, G–H: Wong FRI 32472; D: Hoo HPK 86; E–F: Chan FRI 23816. Drawing by Violette Chye Lay Choon." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8012563/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

